Rating: 2
This wasn't *bad*, other than when the oil in the pan caught fire and all the smoke that poured out of the oven. But I can cope with that. It's just that it wasn't all that good either. It might be worth a shot on a BBQ (that is, outside) but even then, there are tastier things to do with chicken, many of them on this very site. On the bright side: not much work to make this dish at all. If you're not sure, give it a try. You'll have something edible in short time and can decide for yourself. But to me, it's a waste of good ingredients.

