Foolproof crowd pleaser. I made this to the letter and it turned out very well wit rave reviews from everyone. I do not eat chicken myself so was especially pleased that I could pull it off. I agree with the reviewer who suggested that you remove the batteries from your smoke detector, there was a lot of smoke and drama, so try first before you make this one for your local dignitary/celebrity.

